divs: Sighting DetailsI was on holiday with my wife in Scotland, I took lots of pictures, and when I downloaded them to my computer I unfortunately downsized them to save space, it was a few days later when I was looking at the pics that I saw what looks like two bright objects in one of the pic and another bright object in another pic,when I zoomed into the pics they looked saucer shaped, i did not actually notice the objects until I was looking at my pics on the computer. I took the pics in Tyndrum Scotland.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Oban
This sighting has never been favorited.
